data.description: Welcome home! Walk up the front steps onto the covered, oversized porch. Now open the door and come inside of one of Sylvan Hills FINEST!! Upon entering you will be warmly greeted by an endless display of beautiful hardwoods and a quaintly designed open-concept living space. Boasting her stylish, cozy sitting room and amply sized kitchen, adorned by tons of natural lighting, gleaming white cabinetry, granite counters, SS appliances, a huge breakfast bar and a customized pantry! The Owner's ensuite awaits you on the other side presenting a well appointed bedroom with double doors leading to the back deck, a stand alone separate shower and soaking tub, complete with a built-in laundry holder, double vanity and an oversized walk-in closet with customized shelving. The star of the second floor is a huge loft-style flex room ready for you with endless possibilities. There are 2 additional secondary bedrooms, a full bath and a laundry room. Last but certainly not least, the back deck extends the house and overlooks the fully gated, private and secure backyard. Perfect for entertaining. The extended driveway will accommodate 2 SUV's or 3 small cars. The only thing she needs is YOU! Come on home!!
